# Premium E-Wedding Card Refinements

I have completely overhauled the application to incorporate the stunning, premium micro-interactions seen in the reference website, meticulously adapting them to our Mobile-First Kerala aesthetic!

## What Changed

### 1. Global Textures & Glassmorphism
- **Added Grainy Paper Texture:** Embedded a subtle, high-end SVG noise texture directly into the background of `index.css`. This turns flat color into what feels like high GSM expensive physical cardstock.
- **Deep Frosted Glass Tuning:** Updated `.glass-card` styling from a solid `white/92` opacity to a deeply translucent `white/55` with `backdrop-blur-2xl`. The noisy floral background now elegantly bleeds through the edges of the cards.

### 2. Exclusive Pill Badging (`HeroCover.jsx`)
- Replaced the generic "Wedding Invitation" text with a beautifully bordered, rounded pill badge reading **"Exclusive Invitation For [Guest Name]"**.
- Reduced typography tracking heavily to make the large Serif names feel like cohesive, premium calligraphy.

### 3. Date Grid & Inline Countdown (`InsideDetails.jsx`)
- Built an incredible 3-column split Calendar Grid row for the wedding date, replacing the standard list format.
- Integrated the new **Minimal Inline Countdown Timer** flawlessly into the bottom of this grid block, allowing us to safely delete the broken full-page `CountdownTimer.jsx`!

### 4. Tile-Based RSVP System (`RSVPForm.jsx`)
- Refactored the generic buttons into massive interactive Square Tiles.
- Integrated `lucide-react`'s green **Check** and red **X** icons for a massively improved, reference-matching UX.

## Verification
You can now refresh the browser (`http://localhost:5173/`). As you scroll, you'll immediately feel the depth of the new glass textures and notice the sophisticated badging and inline countdown seamlessly integrated into the flow!
